snippet.title: CryptoFights presents: Masumi ⚔🤍
snippet.description:
Fyx Gaming has partnered with Zenescope & Epik.GG to release Masumi on the Fyx NFT Marketplace 💀💙

This NFT includes Masumi + an exclusive digital comic book download!
Get your limited edition CryptoFights skin before it's gone! There are only 1,000 available and once they're sold, they're gone forever~

👇 Link to purchase on Fyx:
https://fyx.live/masumi

👇 Zenescope Official:
https://www.youtube.com/c/zenescopeentertainment

👇 Epik GG:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6oC_SNYkMMTQO4InoSY3Ag
